Package: TomoQC
Type: Package
Title: Simple QC for tomo-seq
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Erik Schild
Maintainer: Erik Schild <erikschild@live.nl>
Description: Provides a simple quality control for tomosequencing experiments. Quality of sample can be assessed per slice, as well as the saturation of sequencing depth of the library.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports:
    stats,
    tibble,
    tidyr,
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    patchwork,
    scales
Example: 
    TomoQC::tomo_quality(example_data$ex_transcripts, example_data$ex_reads, example_data$ex_barcodes, cutoff_spike = 0.2, cutoff_genes = 90, plot_title = "Example output")
